org.jactr.core.buffer.misc

Class ProxyActivationBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jactr.core.utils.DefaultAdaptable
      • org.jactr.core.buffer.AbstractActivationBuffer
        • org.jactr.core.buffer.misc.ProxyActivationBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IActivationBuffer, IAdaptable, IInitializable, IParameterized

    public class ProxyActivationBuffer
extends AbstractActivationBuffer
    a proxy buffer that merely wraps an existing buffer with a new name, and potentially new parameters. Otherwise, the contents will be the same.
    Author:
    harrison
